        <bioghist id="ref9">
            <head>Biographical/Historical Note</head>
            <p>American volunteer nurse in the Italo-Ethiopian War, 1935-1936; photographer and journalist in North Africa, 1936-1939.</p>
        </bioghist>
        <scopecontent id="ref10">
            <head>Scope and Content of Collection</head>
            <p>Correspondence, writings, and photographs, relating to the Italo-Ethiopian War, to Italian colonization of Libya, and to Italian relations in North and East Africa. Includes an album of photographs of Benito Mussolini.</p>
        </scopecontent>
